proposition, namely proposition (a), because the 
constituent (element of the proposition) referred 
to is contained inside the proposition. “The 
cooperative currently employs two people, 
namely Om Oki and Om Herman” is stated in 
Two 
individuals 
were 
referenced in the statement. The two names are 
preceded by honorific markers reserved for 
older men, especially Om Oki and Om Herman. 
The two individuals whose names are preceded 
by honorific marks are referred to as ""they."" 
The relationship between ""they"" and Om Oki 
