Based on comprehensive observations of 
Indonesian Language Textbooks for high school 
level, 2013 curriculum and the Merdeka 
Curriculum, several peace values were found. 
The peace values found are based on references 
from the book Peace Generation: 12 Basic 
Values of Peace by Lincoln and Amalee. The 
research results are described as follows. 
 
