pregnancy at an advanced age, so it needs even 
greater moral support. From the statement of the 
obstetrician Dara, it can be concluded that the 
impact of early pregnancy has a very high risk. 
Pregnancy at an early age is at risk of premature 
birth, low birth weight (LBW), birth bleeding 
that can increase mother and baby mortality.  
