in reducing the rate of destruction caused by 
disasters (Khairunnisa et al., 2021). It is 
important for students to have disaster literacy 
skills in order to understand risks and prepare to 
respond 
effectively 
in 
situations 
(Logayah et al., 2022).  In addition, students 
