There is a significant gap between the 
expected ideal conditions and the actual 
conditions faced by Indonesian society in terms 
of disaster mitigation literacy. Junior high 
school students in Indonesia, including those at 
Pasundan 3 Bandung Junior High School, 
generally do not have adequate disaster 
