Meanwhile, 
the 
effectiveness 
test 
of 
teaching materials was carried out by an 
experimental method with one group pretest-
posttest design. This design includes pretest 
measurements 
followed 
by 
treatment 
and 
posttest for one group (Creswell, 2023). Because 
the data from the test results came from the same 
group (sample), the results of the pretest and 
posttest measurements used a paired sample t-
test on the condition that the data was normally 
distributed. The measurement of this paired 
sample t-test uses the 2022 version of SPSS. 
 
