someone. Saying sorry is a way to convey regret for a 
mistake that We had made. When someone 
apologizes, they are expressing regret for anything 
they have done incorrectly, creating an issue, or 
informing others that they are unable to attend a 
meeting or must leave early, to put it another way, 
attitude 
