Similarities based on pronunciation or sound and 
meaning in vocabulary. Differences based on 
pronunciation and meaning. This research is also 
guided by previous research which discussed 
similar matters, namely contrastive analysis of 
language phonology (Long, 2018; Wang, 1996; 
