since this attribute is usually an abstract item. 
Meanwhile, excerpt (i) evokes the sense that 
Prabowo is identified as a foreign puppet. This 
identification, on the other hand, can be proven 
since the identification exists in the real world. It 
can be seen that this strategy of writing in the 
relational process brings image positively 
toward Joko Widodo and negatively toward 
Prabowo since Prabowo is legitimated while 
Joko Widodo is assumed as a foreign puppet. 
 
Excerpts (j) & (k) also show positive 
