online learning, technology becomes an intrinsic 
element in the learning system. Technology is

 
seen not as the ultimate goal of learning but as a 
solution used to reduce barriers and improve 
interaction and communication between students 
and educators (Bozkurt, 2019). Technological 
readiness and the ability to use various 
