Table 1 and Table 2 shows the variety of 
the structure and the element used to give a 
business name. From the tables, generic element 
plays an important role to construct a phrase in 
bussiness name because the language used in the 
generic element determines how the structure of 
phrase is constructed. Table 3 shows the language 
used in the generic element.  
 
