The masculinity of Arjuna figure 
illustrates in the Javanese Mahabharata story. 
Arjuna has three of the four masculinity 
characters. It indicates that he is a masculine 
man. Following is the description of the three 
masculine characters of Arjuna. 
Be a Big Wheel 
One’s masculinity could be indicated 
by success, power and admiration from 
others. If someone could show these

