results in increased understanding and direction 
(Sari, 2016). 
Gaming Youtubers are utilizing the 
platform’s growth to explore their hobbies by 
creating 
content 
about 
online 
games. 
Additionally, because almost everyone enjoys 
games, these Youtubers have begun to enliven the 
