The increase in average test scores was 
only one indicator of the effectiveness of IMAS 
model implementation in improving students’ 
early reading skills. To further investigate 
model’s effectiveness, correlation and signifi-
cance test were conducted. Table 2 shows the re-
sult of paired-samples correlation test. 
