Table 2 shows that each pair of pretest and 
posttest score had different correlation coeffi-
cient. To calculate the effect of IMAS model im-
plementation in improving each aspect of early 
reading skills, the correlation coefficient for that 
aspect was squared. Significance level (sig.) indi-
